== 製作 ==

=== 拍攝 ===
電影於2016年正式開鏡，並於同年3月在[[臺灣|臺灣]][[臺北市|臺北市]]民生社區三民路一帶取景時，與民生社區居民溝通有所誤會，[[台北市電影委員會|台北市電影委員會]]也出面澄清爭議<ref>{{Cite web|title=魏德聖拍片惹議真相曝光！比「X」並非為了驅離民眾|url=http://movies.ettoday.net/news/663251|author=華少甫|date=2016-03-15|publisher=東森新聞|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315093714/http://movies.ettoday.net/news/663251|archive-date=2016-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/968678|title=魏德聖拍片擾民？ 片商澄清溝通凸槌|author=陳建嘉|date=2016-03-16|publisher=自由時報|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316082355/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/968678|archive-date=2016-03-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=魏導新片封街引不滿？影委會澄清爭議|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160315005799-260404|author=許世穎|date=2016-03-16|publisher=中國時報|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315125525/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160315005799-260404|archive-date=2016-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160314/815925/|title=魏德聖封路拍新片　住戶投訴遭驅離|author=徐卉|date=2016-03-14|publisher=蘋果日報|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318205413/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160314/815925/|archive-date=2016-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=魏德聖北市社區拍片封街 住戶憤投訴|url=http://udn.com/news/story/7262/1563253|author=高睿希|date=2016-03-14|publisher=聯合報|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315183651/http://udn.com/news/story/7262/1563253|archive-date=2016-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年4月，請來[[臺北市市長|臺北市市長]][[柯文哲|柯文哲]]在片中以市長的身分演出一段劇情<ref name="柯文哲">{{Cite web|title=直擊魏德聖河濱拍片　影后耍帥柯P軋一角|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160416/840416/|author=徐卉|date=2016-04-17|publisher=蘋果日報|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421190436/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160416/840416/|archive-date=2016-04-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且拍攝過程十分順利<ref name="柯文哲2">{{Cite web|title=零片酬挺魏德聖音樂片 柯文哲不NG一次過|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1667488|author=陳建嘉|date=2016-04-17|publisher=自由時報|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417125211/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1667488|archive-date=2016-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片耗資8,000萬[[新台幣|新台幣]]，共拍攝39個工作天<ref name="預算">{{Cite web |url = http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160427000708-260112 |title = 讓劇組吃好料 39天殺青 魏德聖導《52 Hz》得意地笑 |author = 林志勳 |date = 2016-04-27 |publisher = 中國時報 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2016-05-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160429133224/http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160427000708-260112 |archive-date = 2016-04-29 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/4/27/n7756018.htm|title=魏德聖推出愛情電影 邊拍邊笑|author=林蘇菲|date=2016-04-27|publisher=大紀元|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2016-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605022353/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/4/27/n7756018.htm|archive-date=2016-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

