== 發行 ==
該片最早在11月5日的北美巡迴放映，第一站於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[蒙特利爾|蒙特利爾]]國家紀念碑劇場舉辦的特映會，由魁北克臺灣青年專業協會（TYPAQ）承辦，演員[[棉花糖_(組合)|小球]]於映後與觀眾互動<ref>{{Cite web |url =http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/11/7/n8468933.htm |title =52Hz，I love you 蒙特利爾特映 初冬傳遞愛意 |author =蔣真 |date =2016-11-08 |publisher =大紀元 |language =zh-hant |accessdate =2017-01-12 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170113132554/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/11/7/n8468933.htm |archive-date =2017-01-13 |dead-url =no }}</ref>。同月19日，導演[[魏德聖|魏德聖]]與演員[[宇宙人_(台灣樂團)|小玉]]在[[美國|美國]][[休斯頓|休斯頓]]舉辦特映會<ref>{{Cite web |url =http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/11/24/n8522842.htm |title =臺灣導演魏德聖新片《52Hz, I love you》休斯頓特映 |author =易永琦 |date =2016-11-24 |publisher =大紀元 |language =zh-hant |accessdate =2017-01-12 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170113132659/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/11/24/n8522842.htm |archive-date =2017-01-13 |dead-url =no }}</ref>。而臺灣定於2017年1月26日在上映<ref>{{Cite web |url =http://star.ettoday.net/news/767793?from=fb_et_star |title =魏德聖「52Hz」片名有洋蔥！「那是世上最寂寞的聲音」 |author =華少甫 |date =2016-09-02 |publisher =娛樂星光雲 |language =zh-hant |accessdate =2016-09-03 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160908105742/http://star.ettoday.net/news/767793?from=fb_et_star |archive-date =2016-09-08 |dead-url =no }}</ref>。此外，《52 Hz I Love You》將於同年12月16日在日本上映<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1128132|title =魏德聖自嘲被蹂躪 掰了音樂片|author =吳琬婷|date =2017-08-19|publisher =[[自由時報|自由時報]]|language =zh-hant|accessdate =2017-08-19|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170819014851/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1128132|archive-date =2017-08-19|dead-url =no}}</ref>。發行後期推出K歌場次，讓演員與影迷同樂刺激票房<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1077371|title =《52赫茲》嗨推K歌場 眾星與影迷同樂|author =吳琬婷|date =2017-02-12|publisher =[[自由時報|自由時報]]|language =zh-hant|accessdate =2017-08-19|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170803212008/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1077371|archive-date =2017-08-03|dead-url =no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《52 Hz I Love You》於首週在全台共收穫2,280萬新台幣，於同期上映的賀歲國片中，電影險勝《[[健忘村|健忘村]]》的2,200萬新台幣，但不敵《[[大釣哥|大釣哥]]》於首週的成績2,400萬新台幣居次<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1074911|title =賀歲國片票房慘跌 破億無望-豬式幽默失靈 52赫茲首戰排名居次|author =吳琬婷|date =2017-02-02|publisher =[[自由時報|自由時報]]|language =zh-hant|accessdate =2017-08-19|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170803211821/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1074911|archive-date =2017-08-03|dead-url =no}}</ref>。2017年2月1日，[[魏德聖|魏德聖]]在受訪時表示，儘管沮喪但沒失去信心，並提到先前《[[海角七號|海角七號]]》的首週成績僅198萬新台幣，是而後憑藉著口碑擴散才創下5.3億新台幣的票房佳績<ref>{{Cite web |url =http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1962351 |title =賀歲國片票房慘 魏德聖盼靠這招再創奇蹟 |date =2017-02-01 |publisher =自由時報 |language =zh-hant |accessdate =2017-08-19 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170803171415/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1962351 |archive-date =2017-08-03 |dead-url =no }}</ref>。最終票房新台幣4,627萬元<ref name="票房">{{cite book |author1=陳斌全總編輯 |title=台灣電影年鑑.2018 |date=2019-01 |publisher=國家電影中心 |location=臺北市 |isbn=978-986-96024-0-2 |pages=p.72-p.161 |edition=初版 |url=https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/中華民國電影年鑑民國107年.pdf |accessdate=2019-04-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514200521/https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%B9%B4%E9%91%91%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B107%E5%B9%B4.pdf |archivedate=2019-05-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

